Bumps <https://github.com/rubocop/rubocop|rubocop> from 1.55.0 to 1.55.1.

Release notes

_Sourced from <https://github.com/rubocop/rubocop/releases|rubocop's releases>._

> *RuboCop 1.55.1*
> *Bug fixes*
> 
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/12068|#12068>: Fix a false positive for `Style/ReturnNilInPredicateMethodDefinition` when the last method argument in method definition is `nil`. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12082|#12082>: Fix an error for `Lint/UselessAssignment` when a variable is assigned and unreferenced in `for` with multiple variables. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12079|#12079>: Fix an error for `Style/MixinGrouping` when mixin method has no arguments. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/11637|#11637>: Correct Rubocop for `private_class_method` method documentation. (<https://github.com/bigzed|`@​bigzed`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/12070|#12070>: Fix false positive in `Style/ArgumentsForwarding` when receiver forwards args/kwargs. (<https://github.com/owst|`@​owst`>)

Changelog

_Sourced from <https://github.com/rubocop/rubocop/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md|rubocop's changelog>._

> *1.55.1 (2023-07-31)*
> *Bug fixes*
> 
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/12068|#12068>: Fix a false positive for `Style/ReturnNilInPredicateMethodDefinition` when the last method argument in method definition is `nil`. ([<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>][])
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12082|#12082>: Fix an error for `Lint/UselessAssignment` when a variable is assigned and unreferenced in `for` with multiple variables. ([<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>][])
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12079|#12079>: Fix an error for `Style/MixinGrouping` when mixin method has no arguments. ([<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>][])
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/11637|#11637>: Correct Rubocop for `private_class_method` method documentation. ([<https://github.com/bigzed|`@​bigzed`>][])
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/12070|#12070>: Fix false positive in `Style/ArgumentsForwarding` when receiver forwards args/kwargs. ([<https://github.com/owst|`@​owst`>][])
